        Clause 4 [<span class="italic">Imposition of borrowing limits</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0648P0-04514'>
        <a name='S5LV0648P0_20030602_GCR_89'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-joan-hanham' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
