      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0648P0-04536'>
        <a name='S5LV0648P0_20030602_GCR_111'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-sally-hamwee' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0648P0_20030602_GCR_111' title='Link to this speech by Ms Sally Hamwee' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-sally-hamwee" title="Ms Sally Hamwee">Baroness Hamwee</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            We support this amendment. Perhaps I should sit down to enable us to get through it before either the noble Lords, Lord Pearson of Rannoch or Lord Stoddart of Swindon, come into the Room and find us discussing the corrupt octopus of Brussels.
